# demo-simulation — decision-informing docs (.md) + transcripts (.txt) are LOCAL ONLY
# (decision-log, spec, digitisation record, captures — they inform later decisions, so per
# the 2026-06-18 policy they are gitignored, not tracked). Also ignore heavy / regenerable /
# customer-adjacent binary media.
demo-simulation/**/*.md
demo-simulation/**/*.txt
#   Videos: Devon's WhatsApp clips + screen recordings (large; reference/
#   customer-adjacent — see spec §9). ** matches the top-level and devon-videos/.
demo-simulation/**/*.mp4
demo-simulation/**/*.mov
demo-simulation/**/*.m4v
#   Chart stills / frame grabs (jpg + png crops).
demo-simulation/devon-videos/stills/
#   Generated validation overlays + plot exports (regenerate from benchvision-app/).
demo-simulation/*.png
#   Generated demo run artefacts — run-record JSON + certificate PDF/PNG (regenerate
#   from benchvision-app/generate_sample_certificates.py / run_demo.py; never tracked).
benchvision-app/demo-output/

